---
/**
 * * About section
 */

import profileImage from "@assets/images/Neorama.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section id="about" class="site-container scroll-mt-10 py-8 md:py-12">
	<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center">
		<div class="md:w-2/3">
			<h2 class="h3 text-primary-500 text-pretty uppercase">The project</h2>
			<h3 class="h2 mt-4">VILLAGE LIVING REBORN IN THE MODERN ERA​​​</h3>
			<div class="bg-base-100 mt-8 p-8 md:mb-20 lg:text-lg">
				<p>
The 'International Village in Northern Greece' project was born as an initiative to establish a vibrant expat community in Greece, modeled after a Greek mediterranean village in the rural area surrounding Thessaloniki, one of the most beautiful cities in Greece and Europe, located just a short drive away. This model will enable participating families to enjoy a lifestyle that many dream of but only a few can afford, while fostering a vibrant and dynamic multi-lingual community.

Life in the community established through this project will fulfill the vision of many families to create a safer, calmer, richer, and more fulfilling future for themselves and their children, all while preserving and nurturing a vibrant communal life.

				</p>
				<div class="flex w-3/4 justify-end">
					<p class="font-heading-1 text-3xl italic"></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mr-auto max-w-md md:w-1/3 md:max-w-none ">
			<div class="my-auto aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden">
				<Image
					src={profileImage}
					alt="Neorama"
					width={450}
					densities={[1.5, 2]}
					class="h-auto w-auto min-w-full object-cover  md:mt-40 "
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
